task.summary: Added crate, crate pane, config wrapper, nbt editor and the serializer
Started the command system. Added the permission enum, added a Locale language file system from mr chocolate, added a debugger and settings for prefix management.
Added the create and remove commands
Added CrateAPI, started the editing gui + GUI Handler System
Added giveall command, listing gui, list command, editing the crate title renaming, added player listeners for quit.
Stable Build, working animations. Touch ups and break case testing left.
Removed unnecessary code. Fixed message error for the give all command, added single user give command.
Removal of crates in hand on use + Giveall and Give command amount bug
Hot fixes to plugin breaking bugs

When clicking the crate in the list GUI, it will be given the player if they have permission. Swapped the <crate> <player> parameters in the give command. Added an option to change the actual crate itemstack name and the crate GUI name to avoid any confusion. Added the list command to help page. And fixed spelling mistakes
